<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="8.[189,310,1257,1283]" box="[189,310,1257,1283]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,310,1257,1283]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,310,1257,1283]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[189,1398,1304,1436]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<taxonomicName authority="Frolov &amp; Akhmetova, 2016" authorityName="Frolov &amp; Akhmetova" authorityYear="2016" box="[189,395,1304,1330]" class="Insecta" family="Orphnidae" genus="Orphnus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="valeriae" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[189,395,1304,1330]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Orphnus valeriae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[402,493,1304,1330]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
is most similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Frolov &amp; Akhmetova, 2016" authorityName="Frolov &amp; Akhmetova" authorityYear="2016" box="[710,843,1304,1330]" class="Insecta" family="Orphnidae" genus="Orphnus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ferrierei" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[710,843,1304,1330]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">O. ferrierei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[850,943,1304,1330]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, but can be separated from it in having pronotum larger and more densely punctate with somewhat elongated punctures, no distinct median longitudinal stria basally on pronotum, frontoclypeal process horn-shaped, and more strongly sclerotized parameres with acute apices (in lateral view).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[189,770,1475,1548]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="8.[189,324,1475,1501]" box="[189,324,1475,1501]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,324,1475,1501]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,324,1475,1501]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[189,770,1521,1548]" box="[189,770,1521,1548]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">We named this species after our daughter Valeria.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
